List of Categories =>
    find all document by type === category
    Show list of categories by Alphabetic Order on Name

List of Discussions by Category =>
    find all document by type === discussion && category === categoryID
    Show list of Discussions by Date (recent first)

List of Posts by Discussion =>
    find all document by type === post && discussions === discussionID
    Show list of Posts by Date (older first)

List of All Discussions =>
    find all document by type === discussion
    Show list of discussions by Date (recent first)
    
Show User profil =>
    find document by type === user && user === userID
    Show user data
    
Add new User =>
    Register Form
    check email and username in document by type === user
    create new document with type user
    
Add new post =>
    create new document with type post
    
Add new Discussion =>
    create new document with type discussions
    
Server : Frigg on NodeJS
Routes for Categories, discussions and User
